defaultre
defaultduction in the use of fungicides and an increase in production as losses to the disease are curtailed.  The company BASF had applied for EU approval of a GM blight-resistant potato but later withdrew the application because of the difficult EU situation.
default 
defaultT
defaulthe full potential contribution of GM production to the UK will clearly depend on the range of new crop traits that might be developed and adopted over time.    
